import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='delay', kde=True, color='blue', bins=30)
    plt.axvline(data['delay'].median(), color='red', linestyle='--', label=f"Median: {data['delay'].median():.2f}")
    plt.title("What is the distribution of flight delays?", wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel("Delay (minutes)")
    plt.ylabel("Frequency")
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['date'])]
    
    avg_delay = data.groupby('origin')['delay'].mean().reset_index()
    chart = sns.barplot(x='origin', y='delay', data=avg_delay)
    plt.title('What is the average delay time for each origin airport?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Origin Airport')
    plt.ylabel('Average Delay Time')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['origin_destination'] = data['origin'] + '-' + data['destination']
    origin_destination_counts = data['origin_destination'].value_counts().reset_index()
    origin_destination_counts.columns = ['origin_destination', 'count']
    origin_destination_counts['origin'] = origin_destination_counts['origin_destination'].str.split('-').str[0]
    origin_destination_counts['destination'] = origin_destination_counts['origin_destination'].str.split('-').str[1]
    origin_destination_pivot = origin_destination_counts.pivot('origin', 'destination', 'count').fillna(0)

    plt.figure(figsize=(12, 12))
    sns.heatmap(origin_destination_pivot, cmap='coolwarm', annot=True, fmt='.0f', linewidths=.5)
    plt.title('What is the most common origin and destination airport pair?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Destination')
    plt.ylabel('Origin')
    plt.legend(title='Count', loc='upper left', bbox_to_anchor=(1, 1))
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
